This article describes the use of Sony DualShock 3 / [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sixaxis Sixaxis] and DualShock 4 [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PlayStation PlayStation] controllers via USB and Bluetooth.

== Prerequisites ==
This article assumes that [[USB]] and [[Bluetooth]] have been previously configured.

== Hardware ==
* DualShock 3 / Sixaxis
