</pre>}}

== Kernel ==
The recommended minimum version of Linux to use is 3.15. This release adds full support for the DualShock 4. This release also fixes the DualShock 3 blinking LED issue when connected via Bluetooth.<ref>LKML, [https://lkml.org/lkml/2014/4/2/264 "HID layer pull request"]</ref>

